This software bundles YARA rules from the following third-party sources
at image build time. Each source retains its own license:

1. YARA-Forge (core/extended/full bundle)
   URL:     https://github.com/YARAHQ/yara-forge
   License: mixed (each contributing ruleset retains its own license;
            see the YARA-Forge repository for the per-rule attribution)

2. Neo23x0/signature-base
   URL:     https://github.com/Neo23x0/signature-base
   License: Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International
            (CC BY-NC 4.0)

3. ANY.RUN YARA Rules
   URL:     https://github.com/anyrun/YARA
   License: MIT

4. DidierStevens/DidierStevensSuite (curated OLE/RTF/maldoc rules)
   URL:     https://github.com/DidierStevens/DidierStevensSuite
   License: Public Domain ("Source code put in public domain by Didier
            Stevens, no Copyright")

5. bartblaze/Yara-rules
   URL:     https://github.com/bartblaze/Yara-rules
   License: MIT

6. InQuest/yara-rules-vt (curated selection)
   URL:     https://github.com/InQuest/yara-rules-vt
   License: MIT

7. Local rules (yarad)
   URL:     https://github.com/eilandert/rspamd-yarad
   License: MIT (same as this project)

